metadata.name: Crypto Friesians Foundation NFT Collection #1
metadata.description: Welcome to The House of Friesian Stud (HOFS) Crypto Friesians 10,000 Foundation NFT Collection. This collection is the 1st series of unique utility-enabled PFP's. Each NFT represents a Rare Royal Dutch Studbook Friesian physically owned IRL by HOFS. Future utility functions associated with the NFT will be designed, then dropped in the NFT Owner's wallet for deployment and utility across HOFS Friesian Studfarms and Metaverse. The selection of Friesian horse images generated will ONLY BE AVAILABLE in the HOFS Foundation Collection - Introducing Truus, Taapke, Galterio and Lancelot. Mint The Herd!
metadata.creator: Leonie Margaret Campbell
